<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/school_header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="disclosure-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Mandatory Public Disclosure</h1>
                <p>Ensuring transparency and compliance with educational regulatory requirements.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="disclosure-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Commitment to Transparency and Compliance</h2>
                <p>N.R.K. Public School is dedicated to maintaining the highest standards of transparency and compliance as mandated by various educational regulatory bodies, including the Central Board of Secondary Education (CBSE). This section provides access to important public documents and information about our school.</p>
                <p>We believe in open communication with our stakeholders – parents, students, and the community – and strive to make all necessary information easily accessible.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="disclosure-documents-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Key Disclosure Documents</h2>
                <p>Below is a list of documents available for public viewing. Click on the links to download the respective PDF files.</p>
                <div class="disclosure-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/1_school_info.pdf" target="_blank">1. General Information of the School</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/2_noc.pdf" target="_blank">2. Copy of No Objection Certificate (NOC) issued by State Govt./UT Administration</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/3_recognition.pdf" target="_blank">3. Copy of Recognition Certificate under RTE Act, 2009</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/4_building_safety.pdf" target="_blank">4. Copy of Building Safety Certificate</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/5_fire_safety.pdf" target="_blank">5. Copy of Fire Safety Certificate</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/6_sanitation.pdf" target="_blank">6. Copy of Sanitation Certificate</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/7_staff_list.pdf" target="_blank">7. List of Teachers and Staff (including details of qualification, experience, etc.)</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/8_fee_structure.pdf" target="_blank">8. Details of Fee Structure</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/9_academic_calendar.pdf" target="_blank">9. Academic Calendar</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/10_smc_list.pdf" target="_blank">10. List of School Management Committee (SMC) Members</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/documents/disclosure/11_transfer_certificate.pdf" target="_blank">11. Transfer Certificate Rules and Sample</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <p class="note"><em>Please note that these documents are provided in PDF format for easy viewing and download. For any further clarification or detailed information, please contact the school administration.</em></p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Need More Information?</h2>
                <p>Our administrative staff can assist you with any questions regarding these disclosures.</p>
                <a href="/school/contact" class="cta-button primary">Contact School Administration</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>